Welcome to the start of the 2009 Championship tournament. The top 16 wrestlers of the season face off in a single elimination tournament. Check out the Summer Vengeance Bracket here.
Hollie Stevens finished this year ranked 10th, After taking last season off, this veteran returned and did not lose a step. She is a power to reckon with.
Yana Jordan joined Ultimate Surrender this year. She finished her rookie season ranked 10th, which is an amazing accomplishment. Yana is skilled in ground fighting, but is still struggling from the bottom position.
This was a brutal match, with both wrestlers taking a pounding as their bodies clashed in unscripted wrestling. In the end Hollie tied up Yana with her own bands and vibrated the loser to orgasm after orgasm on the mat.
